        <div xml:id="TK585">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>kaṭāa uruvoṭu kaṇṇañcā tiyāṇṭu </l>
<l> mukāamai vallatē yoṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>A spy is one who is able to assume an appearance which may create no suspicion (in the minds of others), who fears no man's face, and who never reveals (his purpose).</l>
            </lg>
